description: Returns a list that contains the number of managed Contributor Insights rules in your account.

parameters.name: ResourceARN
parameters.description: The ARN of an Amazon Web Services resource that has managed Contributor Insights rules.

nested_items.name: ManagedRules
nested_items.description: The managed rules that are available for the specified Amazon Web Services resource.

nested_items.name: TemplateName
nested_items.description: The template name for the managed rule. Used to enable managed rules using PutManagedInsightRules.

nested_items.name: ResourceARN
nested_items.description: If a managed rule is enabled, this is the ARN for the related Amazon Web Services resource.

nested_items.name: RuleState
nested_items.description: Describes the state of a managed rule. If present, it contains information about the Contributor Insights rule that contains information about the related Amazon Web Services resource.

nested_items.name: RuleName
nested_items.description: The name of the Contributor Insights rule that contains data for the specified Amazon Web Services resource.

nested_items.name: State
nested_items.description: Indicates whether the rule is enabled or disabled.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: Include this value to get the next set of rules if the value was returned by the previous operation.
